{"tid":2361158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"零下16度街頭實測舌頭奶鐵柱 少年玩出禍「舌柱合一」分不開","createTime":"2021-01-10T11:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T13:08:43.000Z","uid":50386,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"128b448c90c86a4beca07d983f3c9a42e44562e9","tid":2361158,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:48:41.000Z","msg":"寒流來襲，香港近幾天的溫度都徘徊在10度左右，而內地部份城市的氣溫更降至零下，不少人在寒冬下可能都不想出街，不過山東有位少年在好奇心驅使下，竟然想實驗在負16度的寒冬下用舌頭舔鐵柱是否真的會「黏住」，沒想到直接上演「舌柱合一」！<br />\n<br />\n綜合支那媒體報導，山東有位15歲少年在零下16度的氣溫下進行街頭實驗，他聽聞在低溫下如果用舌頭舔鐵柱，舌頭有機會被黏住，於是他趁工作空檔時親自落街實測。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQYAMbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQYAMbk.png&h=fcf01d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他一臉輕鬆地走到鐵柱前，先呼出幾口暖氣，然後實驗正式開始，伸出舌頭舔鐵柱，怎料不用幾秒，舌頭真的跟鐵柱黏實，拔不下來，令他動彈不得，嚇得他隨即打電話給同事求救，張開着嘴巴叫：「救我！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sEUHrbw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsEUHrbw.png&h=f060b958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然而，由於少年口齒不清，同事因為聽不清楚而收線，過了一會兒，有好心人見狀而拿熱水來迎救，及時澆在少年的舌頭上，才令少年的舌頭跟鐵柱成功分開，事後少年的舌頭只有少許麻痺，並無大礙。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R94z1K3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR94z1K3.png&h=b5bc737f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n少年「做實驗」的整個過程剛好被附近的閉路電視拍到，影片在網上曝光，引來不少網友無情恥笑，有人留言：「少年這麼想不開？」、「我小時候都有這樣想過，但真的不敢做出來。」、「外國不乏這樣的案例吧！」、「要試在家裡用冰塊試不好嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cTxNlhIU-cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcTxNlhIU-cc&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7U4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=3134c6ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cTxNlhIU-cc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3c746a7d83b62b4a8f59743c59f9da57916f84","tid":2361158,"uid":257914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554208d1c8e0d11d3d881cc572ba6c5d6395affd","tid":2361158,"uid":199893,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"On9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4557a4c36a145ffe6298c6b73d3b4ecabec5ae","tid":2361158,"uid":200083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e7aa7c89cac762cb239d53c095f973141b1ad5","tid":2361158,"uid":49784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:02:54.000Z","msg":"講左好多年唔好咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965544f9eb840bd0fd0d519a53d1e8e313a69b9c","tid":2361158,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:18:29.000Z","msg":"有好心人見狀而拿熱水來迎救，及時澆在少年的舌頭上<br />\n<br />\n遲早出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babb960d5ec7a8a6b9e60d040d147d449619eac6","tid":2361158,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T12:43:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7a003a9ae6b7f6d0798342d6217e2baf2e3b4b","tid":2361158,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci